title: 12/20 Fantasy Football Podcast: Week 16 Tough Calls; "Hey, Real Quick"
description:
Do you need a contingency plan if you're looking to start any Eagles this week (2:50)? PHI could have the #1 seed locked up before this week's game ... Recapping the Waiver Wire (5:55) before we look ahead to 2018 with some "Hey, Real Quick" (21:16)! Deshaun Watson or Carson Wentz? Jimmy Graham or Jordan Howard? ... Week 16 tough calls! How are we feeling about DeMaryius Thomas (24:15), A.J. Green (26:20), Jordan Howard (29:01), Dak Prescott (32:34) and more? Then stay tuned for some awesome NFL/Fantasy analysis from our Senior NFL Columnist Pete Prisco (45:35) as he dishes on Julio Jones, what to expect from Ezekiel Elliott in his first game back, if Blake Bortles is legit and more ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
